<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>add "glacier picture" check box to View control panel
<li>integrate new background image with proper perspective
<li>change drop constraints for Glacial Budget Meter, snap to surface of glacier or valley, display "?" while dragging
<li>fix so that debris continues to be generated after Restart or Reset All
<li>fix title on "Graphs" control panel
<li>move origin indicator on thermometer to be vertically aligned with center of bulb
</ul>
<p>
<b>Known problems:</b>
<ul>
<li>debris is appearing on the glacier's surface above the ELA, model problem
<li>glacier advances too rapidly, model problem
</ul>
<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<ul>
<li>ice doesn't appear to move
<li>snowfall is not visible
<li>time-based graphs are not implemented
<li>features need to be split into Basic and Advanced panels
<li>no Help menu option to show pictures of real glaciers
</ul>
